text: Tuovi Sappinen is a Finnish gymnast. Tuovi competed in six events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. She was born on April 8, 1941 in Turku.Tuovi Sappinen == References == Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:Gymnasts Category:Olympians for Finland Category:Sportspeople from Turku
